## Data and Code Availability
This folder contains the scripts used to process the data and generate the tables and figures reported in "Wisselen van werkgever, maar ook van bedrijfstak?",
published on May 28, 2026. It also contains the derived datasets underlying the published results. The original microdata used in this study are CBS microdata. 
This data is confidential and cannot be made publicly available due to legal and privacy restrictions. 
This repository therefore does not include the underlying confidential microdata.

## Reuse and citation
The materials in this repository (code and derived data) are provided to support transparency and reproducibility of the research.
Users are free to use these materials for research and other purposes, provided that appropriate academic credit is given. 
If you use the data, code, or other materials from this repository, please cite the associated publication:
Volkerink, M., Ruland, A., & Biesenbeek, C. (2026). Wisselen van werkgever, maar ook van bedrijfstak? 
Een empirische analyse van sectorale arbeidsmobiliteit (DNB Analyse). De Nederlandsche Bank.

## Notes
- Derived datasets correspond to the data underlying the tables and figures in the publication.
- Scripts are provided to document the data processing and analysis steps.
- The repository is provided “as is”, without warranty of any kind.
